openapi-spec-forge

To generate fast, static API docs from your OpenAPI 3.x spec. Zero dependencies, single HTML
output, deployable anywhere — S3, CDN, or local. Built to handle big endpoint APIs without the
browser-hanging bulk of tools.


USAGE

  uv venv
  source .venv/bin/activate

  ./bin/build -i openapi.json
  ./bin/build -i openapi.json -o docs/index.html -t "My API"


OPTIONS

  -i, --input       Path to OpenAPI 3.x JSON file (required)
  -o, --output      Output HTML file            (default: api-docs.html)
  -t, --title       Page title override         (default: from spec)
      --base-url    Override server base URL    (default: from spec)
      --no-embed-data   Write spec as a separate .data.json file
      --no-inline-js    Write JS/CSS as separate files


